embodied in the
agreement, we will only get to
part of where

30:19.284 --> 30:21.119 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
we need to go.

30:21.153 --> 30:26.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But make no mistake, this
agreement will help
delay or avoid some of the worst
consequences

30:26.958 --> 30:28.193 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of climate change.

30:28.226 --> 30:31.063 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Hillary Clinton
