This was a site in Hawaii.

33:32.143 --> 33:33.778 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GAVIN SCHMIDT: That's right.

33:33.812 --> 33:35.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: They say it's
