34:07.078 --> 34:08.780 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GAVIN SCHMIDT: It's a big deal.

34:08.813 --> 34:14.019 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, you're saying
it's a big
deal, but you can't get
discouraged about

34:14.052 --> 34:15.887 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
